name: KEM Open Source
body:
### Welcome to KEM Open Source
KEM release open source code to help you take full advantage of our fulfilment services.

## Repos
# Duka
![Duka](http://img.kem.guru/store/logo/0/100/100/logo-duka)

Duka, Swahili for *shop*, is a fully functional eCommerce website fully using the KEM Api. Hosted on bitbucket to allow free, private forks, it is released under the MIT license.
[https://bitbucket.org/kemsolutions/duka](https://bitbucket.org/kemsolutions/duka)
